{"tid":436200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"往機場塞爆棄車 青衣區公路現拖篋人潮","createTime":"2017-10-15T03:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T04:54:47.000Z","uid":42188,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"26430465f70da21d4ebd3fb6df0ad55ab175354d","tid":436200,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"颱風卡努襲港，天文台於早上8時40分改發8號東北烈風或暴風訊號。受到風暴影響，青馬大橋、汀九橋、昂船洲大橋及青嶼幹線都有封路等強風管制措施，所有車輛需改行青馬大橋下層出入機場及禁止使用馬灣路出入馬灣，同時長青隧道去機場需要間封，導致青馬管制區一帶入機場的交通今早嚴重擠塞，往機場的巴士排出一字長龍。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示，由於車多關係，青嶼幹線來回方向、長青公路往機場方向、長青隧道往機場方向、青衣北岸公路往機場方向，及北大嶼山公路往九龍方向，交通擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n由於現場交通大混亂，大批乘搭公共交通工具往機場的市民，當中不乏空姐等機艙服務員，在青衣塞車塞了個多小時，仍未能離開青衣，不少人隨即帶同行李下車，在公路拉著行李篋離開現場，改為步行至附近的港鐵站繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n趕搭12點機的李先生指，由於塞車塞了「大半個鐘」，見可步行約一小時往青衣機鐵站，遂落車行，「好彩冇雨落。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/111233_a87f6ce6a2a705594b43f66e2fee19fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F111233_a87f6ce6a2a705594b43f66e2fee19fc.jpg&h=458137ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/111242_35d0d4e25e1bcf61b9e16bbf70c1510e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F111242_35d0d4e25e1bcf61b9e16bbf70c1510e.jpg&h=4bb42f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/111251_1bdcbcccfc99c85f79208bf96f1b8557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F111251_1bdcbcccfc99c85f79208bf96f1b8557.jpg&h=365f4944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/111259_3beddae7e0667de906c18f44ea34c7ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F111259_3beddae7e0667de906c18f44ea34c7ab.jpg&h=98cfcbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知有幾多UO撚貪平坐巴士而miss飛機，因小失大</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ca75111dfdcb3c4eebea1bd5aea17095440ea2","tid":436200,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af99032c495b236d0f7217a330c79eb097fea25a","tid":436200,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對黑絲一定好臭"},{"pid":"a75afb77b685039f25acd54b622a0e1afee451c5","tid":436200,"uid":1494,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"去機場坐巴士係最好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d256fb7b8bc5bbc3a3b7373838af7b74d5ed57","tid":436200,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:30:17.000Z","msg":"咁急去機場都冇用，八號波都唔會飛啦"},{"pid":"84a4819b0d9b647403a85a7c7c30e0a010f573db","tid":436200,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去機場坐巴士係最好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明知8號風球就唔好坐巴士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fa18e33109a512beedb696cee1648f9f3cf45f","tid":436200,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁急去機場都冇用，八號波都唔會飛啦</blockquote><br />\n你錯啦 可以照飛的"},{"pid":"8b9a27381d988230e65c2f1cca67cf33033f60f7","tid":436200,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"對黑絲腳係咁行路浸腳味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"